1
00:00:00,520 --> 00:00:01,280
While you're away

2
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:02,160
Get dressed and escape

3
00:00:04,760 --> 00:00:05,960
You're quite honest

4
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:08,160
There are passwords for entry and exit here

5
00:00:08,640 --> 00:00:09,920
Do you think you can escape

6
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:11,160
What do you want to do

7
00:00:13,280 --> 00:00:14,120
What do I want to do

8
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:17,080
We are husband and wife

9
00:00:18,931 --> 00:00:19,927
What do you think I want to do

10
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,280
You killed my father

11
00:00:23,720 --> 00:00:25,280
Do you think I will like you

12
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:27,650
Of course I can

13
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:28,560
Jiajia

14
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,352
From now on

15
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,800
Your world will only have me

16
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:36,160
You can hate me

17
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:37,600
But I also

18
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,920
will make you love me beyond control

19
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,320
Let me go

20
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:50,935
Jiajia

21
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:53,360
We will have a new start

22
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,760
I will treat you well

23
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,760
As long as you forget the past

24
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,360
We will live a happy life

25
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:01,840
Yes

26
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,720
We could have been very happy

27
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:05,920
But why

28
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,360
did you do that to my father

29
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,800
He is my father

30
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,680
It was your father who courted death

31
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,440
He threatened me

32
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,551
If I didn't marry into the Ni family

33
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,240
he would expose my identity

34
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,280
and make me lose everything

35
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:22,520
Yet marrying you was not enough

36
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:24,080
He also asked me to transfer to him

37
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,760
10% of Zhou's company shares

38
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:28,480
Am I supposed to be

39
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:30,256
constantly held by the throat and drained of blood by him

40
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,135
You admit it

41
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,680
You are not Zhou Xubai

42
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,660
This was not yours originally

43
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,280
It was you who had evil intentions

44
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,944
and killed the real Zhou Xubai

45
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,000
And took his place